      "source": [
        "# üìå Step 5: Transformations\n",
        "# Convert 'purchased' to categorical\n",
        "df['purchased'] = df['purchased'].astype('category')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Create age groups\n",
        "bins = [18, 25, 35, 45, 60]\n",
        "labels = ['18-24', '25-34', '35-44', '45-60']\n",
        "df['age_group'] = pd.cut(df['age'], bins=bins, labels=labels, right=False)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "j2HEj1e-LqKz"
      },
      "execution_count": 5,
